  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research study is to understand the effect of a short mindfulness video&#xD;
      on self perceived performance in the OR. Specifically, assessing the effectiveness of brief&#xD;
      mindfulness intervention on physician focus, anxiety and perceived performance at the time of&#xD;
      a procedure through a survey containing a modified flow state scale and modified applied&#xD;
      mindfulness process scale&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
