  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Perceived flow</measure>
    <time_frame>At the end of the procedure, up to 5 hours</time_frame>
    <description>Perceived flow will be assessed using a modified flow state scale after case. Items are rated from Strongly disagree to Strongly agree. Items are summed and scored.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>Perceived application of mindfulness</measure>
    <time_frame>at the end of the procedure, up to 5 hours</time_frame>
    <description>Perceived mindfulness will be assess using a modified applied mindfulness process scale. Items are rated never, rarely, sometimes, often and always. Items are summed and scored.</description>
  </secondary_outcome>
